Summer school ERMITES

"Scaled Audiovisual Information Retrieval"

24, 25, 26 sept 2013 - =EEle de Porquerolles - Var - France
pre-proceedings : http://sis.univ-tln.fr/~glotin/Actes_ERMITES2013_V06.pdf

Prog. :
* S. Bengio, Google, USA, 'Large Scale Image/Music Understanding'
* C. Schmid, INRIA, LEAR, France, 'Actions Recognition from Videos:
some Recent Results'
* B. Caputo, IDIAP EPFL, Switzerland, 'Learning to Learn in Computer
Vision & Robotics'
* J. Sanchez, Cordoba univ., Argentina, 'Fisher Vectors for Classification'
* M. Cord, LIP6, France, 'Beyond Bag of Visual Word Model for Image
